tor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">O que \u00e9 Core Business?\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7989f7e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7989f7e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3bc282 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a3bc282\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.16.0 - 20-09-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">O core business, tamb\u00e9m conhecido como &#8220;neg\u00f3cio central&#8221;, \u00e9 o cerne da atividade de uma empresa. Trata-se da principal \u00e1rea de atua\u00e7\u00e3o que define a miss\u00e3o e estrat\u00e9gia da organiza\u00e7\u00e3o. Em outras palavras, o core business \u00e9 o foco central que sustenta a empresa e \u00e9 crucial para o seu sucesso. \u00c9 a atividade principal e distintiva que a empresa executa no mercado.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1781574 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1781574\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6fd9c0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b6fd9c0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">A import\u00e2ncia do Core Business\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01f3725 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"01f3725\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1f426a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1f426a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Clareza de prop\u00f3sito<\/strong><\/p><p>Quando uma empresa identifica com precis\u00e3o sua atividade central, ela obt\u00e9m uma vis\u00e3o clara de seu prop\u00f3sito. Isso direciona os recursos, esfor\u00e7os e investimentos para as \u00e1reas essenciais e relevantes. Ter uma vis\u00e3o n\u00edtida do que \u00e9 fundamental permite tomar decis\u00f5es estrat\u00e9gicas mais acertadas.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d6a1d1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4d6a1d1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11cc731 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"11cc731\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Competitividade<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Focar no core business permite que a empresa se torne mais competitiva. Ao se especializar naquilo em que \u00e9 verdadeiramente especialista, a organiza\u00e7\u00e3o pode se destacar no mercado, superando a concorr\u00eancia. Isso se traduz em uma vantagem competitiva s\u00f3lida.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-439a9eb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"439a9eb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-440ffdc elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"440ffdc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>\u00a0Efici\u00eancia operacional<\/strong><\/p><p>Quando uma empresa direciona seus recursos para suas atividades principais, ela consegue aprimorar suas opera\u00e7\u00f5es e processos. Isso resulta em redu\u00e7\u00e3o de custos e aumento da efici\u00eancia, pois a organiza\u00e7\u00e3o est\u00e1 constantemente melhorando o que faz de forma excepcional.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24d3f58 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"24d3f58\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c5e8a6 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c5e8a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Estrat\u00e9gia de longo prazo<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A defini\u00e7\u00e3o do core business \u00e9 essencial para o desenvolvimento de uma estrat\u00e9gia de longo prazo s\u00f3lida. Isso ajuda a empresa a estabelecer metas e dire\u00e7\u00f5es claras para o futuro. Uma estrat\u00e9gia bem fundamentada no core business \u00e9 fundamental para o crescimento sustent\u00e1vel e a prosperidade cont\u00ednua.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66da9be e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"66da9be\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d347855 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d347855\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Tomada de Decis\u00e3o<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Entender o core business facilita a tomada de decis\u00e3o. A empresa pode avaliar se uma oportunidade de neg\u00f3cio ou projeto est\u00e1 alinhada com sua \u00e1rea central de atua\u00e7\u00e3o antes de investir recursos. Isso ajuda a evitar distra\u00e7\u00f5es e desvios desnecess\u00e1rios da estrat\u00e9gia principal.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af3d5d2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"af3d5d2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7880186 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7880186\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Exemplos de Core Business\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca2f395 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ca2f395\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-715324f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"715324f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">O core business varia de acordo com o setor e a natureza da empresa. Aqui est\u00e3o alguns exemplos de core business em diferentes segmentos:<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-102239f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"102239f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd1405f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cd1405f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>1. Apple Inc.<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Apple \u00e9 amplamente conhecida por seu core business: o design, desenvolvimento e venda de produtos eletr\u00f4nicos, como iPhones, iPads, MacBooks e software relacionado. A empresa concentra seus esfor\u00e7os na cria\u00e7\u00e3o de dispositivos inovadores e na experi\u00eancia do usu\u00e1rio.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8301a6d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8301a6d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c50533 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c50533\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2. Google<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">O <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google<\/a> concentra-se em seu core business de pesquisa na internet e publicidade online. A maior parte de sua receita \u00e9 gerada por meio de an\u00fancios na pesquisa e na plataforma do YouTube. A empresa aprimora constantemente suas tecnologias de pesquisa e publicidade.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3564bc5 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3564bc5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ab089e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5ab089e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>3. Coca-Cola<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Coca-Cola concentra-se na fabrica\u00e7\u00e3o e distribui\u00e7\u00e3o de bebidas n\u00e3o alco\u00f3licas, como refrigerantes e sucos. Este \u00e9 o cora\u00e7\u00e3o do seu neg\u00f3cio, e a empresa trabalha continuamente para expandir sua presen\u00e7a global no mercado de bebidas.4<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6fd3dd4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6fd3dd4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51e0e95 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"51e0e95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>4. McDonald&#8217;s<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A principal atividade da McDonald&#8217;s \u00e9 a opera\u00e7\u00e3o de restaurantes de fast food. Este \u00e9 o cerne do seu neg\u00f3cio, e tudo o que fazem gira em torno dessa atividade. A empresa se especializa em oferecer alimentos r\u00e1pidos e acess\u00edveis aos consumidores.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8f530db e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8f530db\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;: