cc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc76646 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fc76646\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Analise a miss\u00e3o e vis\u00e3o: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Comece analisando a miss\u00e3o e a vis\u00e3o da sua empresa. Esses documentos geralmente oferecem insights sobre o prop\u00f3sito e os objetivos fundamentais da organiza\u00e7\u00e3o. A miss\u00e3o e a vis\u00e3o devem refletir o core business da empresa.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-86e576b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"86e576b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a921ff2 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a921ff2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Identifique os produtos e servi\u00e7os principais: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Identifique os produtos ou servi\u00e7os que geram a maior parte da receita da sua empresa. Estes s\u00e3o os produtos ou servi\u00e7os essenciais que <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">contribuem <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">significativamente para o sucesso do neg\u00f3cio. Avalie quais deles est\u00e3o alinhados com a miss\u00e3o da empresa e qual deles \u00e9 central para a sua identidade.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4317cde e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4317cde\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd74ce7 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bd74ce7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Avalie o mercado: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analise o mercado em que a empresa atua. Quais s\u00e3o as principais necessidades dos clientes que a empresa atende? Quais s\u00e3o os segmentos de mercado mais relevantes para o core business? Considere tamb\u00e9m o mercado futuro e se as atividades atuais da empresa est\u00e3o alinhadas com as tend\u00eancias emergentes.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-868cfd9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"868cfd9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a13b63 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1a13b63\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Considere a concorr\u00eancia: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analise as atividades dos concorrentes. O que eles fazem bem? Como voc\u00ea se diferencia deles? Identifique quais atividades s\u00e3o \u00fanicas para a sua empresa e que representam a sua especializa\u00e7\u00e3o.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-257870c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"257870c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21eab1b elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"21eab1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Identifique as compet\u00eancias essenciais: <\/b>Q<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">uais s\u00e3o as compet\u00eancias e recursos que a sua empresa possui e que a tornam \u00fanica e competitiva no mercado? Essas compet\u00eancias essenciais s\u00e3o aquelas que s\u00e3o fundamentais para o sucesso da empresa no seu core business.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-afd75e0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"afd75e0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2a1637 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a2a1637\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Esteja disposto a evoluir: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">O core business de uma empresa pode evoluir ao longo do tempo \u00e0 medida que o mercado muda. Esteja disposto <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">a reavaliar e ajustar sua defini\u00e7\u00e3o de core business q